<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy | VerticaSoft Email Service</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-50 font-[Inter]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <a href="/" class="text-indigo-600 font-bold mb-8 inline-block">← Back to Home</a>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <div class="prose prose-indigo max-w-none text-gray-600 space-y-6">
            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>At VerticaSoft Email Service, we take your privacy and the privacy of your email recipients seriously. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard data in our role as an infrastructure provider for transactional emails.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Data We Collect</h2>
                <p>We collect information necessary to provide our services, including:</p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                    <li>Account information (Name, Email, Organization)</li>
                    <li>Technical data (IP addresses, API keys, Domain verification records)</li>
                    <li>Transactional metadata (Recipient email, timestamp, delivery status, bounce/complaint data)</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. Use of Recipient Data</h2>
                <p>Recipient email addresses are used ONLY for the purpose of delivering the messages you send via our API. We do not sell, rent, or use recipient data for marketing purposes. Data provided to us is strictly used for infrastructure delivery and bounce/complaint management.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Compliance with AWS SES Policies</h2>
                <p>Our infrastructure is powered by AWS SES. We adhere to all AWS Acceptable Use Policies. We monitor bounce and complaint rates to maintain high sender reputation and comply with anti-spam regulations.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Security</h2>
                <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including API key authentication, TLS encryption for emails in transit, and secure storage of account metadata.</p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@verticasoft.com.</p>
            </section>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200 text-gray-400 text-sm">
            Last updated: March 23, 2026
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
